{"name": "Blueberry DAO #1","description": "Welcome to Blueberry DAO, a community owned and driven, decentralised autonomous organisation (DAO) focused on supporting children's charities and initiatives for children in need. Blueberry DAO is the creation of 13 year old Lilpurpberry with the help of a community grant from Nouns DAO and Nouncil.

By purchasing a token p'8, you're helping to fund proposals put forth by DAO members to make a real difference in the lives of children. As a token holder, you have the power to participate in DAO governance by voting on proposals to support children's causes or submitting your own!

Join us in our mission to create a brighter future for children in need. Together, we can change lives.

Blueberry DAO is a creation by Lilpurpberry, with the help of her father ThaSwami and a generous community grant provided by Nouncil, delegated grants from Nouncillors and NounsDAO.","image": "https://api.zora.co/renderer/stack-images?contractAddress=0xf8f977d82b298e83464357efe58538f608834185&tokenId=1&images=ipfs%3a%2f%2fbafybeib3vm72ktu5auyyq24pfinb466mu627pewfi2x2mpvkmzad6vogqa%2f0backgrounds%2fbg-yellow.svg&images=ipfs%3a%2f%2fbafybeib3vm72ktu5auyyq24pfinb466mu627pewfi2x2mpvkmzad6vogqa%2f1bodies%2fbody-chocolate.svg&images=ipfs%3a%2f%2fbafybeib3vm72ktu5auyyq24pfinb466mu627pewfi2x2mpvkmzad6vogqa%2f2hearts%2fheart-sky.svg&images=ipfs%3a%2f%2fbafybeib3vm72ktu5auyyq24pfinb466mu627pewfi2x2mpvkmzad6vogqa%2f3glasses%2fglasses-square-teal.svg","properties": {"0backgrounds": "bg-yellow","1bodies": "body-chocolate","2hearts": "heart-sky","3glasses": "glasses-square-teal"}}
